      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a meticulous service history, including preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis is pristine with no subframe fatigue, and the M-DCT transmission delivers crisp, rev-matched downshifts. Finished in flawless factory paint over Novillo leather, the cabin remains factory-fresh with zero bolster wear. Mechanically, the VANOS system is silent, and the EDC suspension retains its original damping characteristics. A turn-key performance icon for the purist.",
